!! Verb inflection
!  ---------------
!! The Burmese language verbs inflect.

! Lexicon containing POS tag only:
LEXICON V
+V: V-suff ;

! Lexicon containing inflectional suffixes and corresponding tags:
LEXICON V-suff
+Realis+Nom:တာ   # ;
+Realis:တယ်  # ;
+Irrealis:မယ် # ;
+Irrealis+Nom:မှာ    # ;;

! vim: set ft=xfst-lexc:

